metadata.name: fmfers #1
metadata.description: Our artist is the lesser-known brother from another father of Vitalik Buterin, Virtalik Butthurtin. They are both mfers as well as their parents. His brother Vitalik, is an OG stickman and does not give a shit about what you think about him coz mfer is conquering the world in his own gwei. Virtalik, on the other hand, is the creative expressive one, who likes to scribble. Inspired by his distant cousin, Sartoshi, Virtalik plans to change the world 1 line at time.
